title: Ep - 91 - TOM SANDOVAL FROM VANDERPUMP RULES
description:
Tom Sandoval from Vanderpump Rules discusses how he ended up in Los Angeles, what really happened between Faith and Jax, supporting a partner who has been the victim of abuse, and the new restaurant Tom Tom he is opening with Tom Schwartz and Lisa Vanderpump. 


Lindsay Hubbard from Summer House explains why she and Everett broke up, what really happened in the house this summer, and what to expect from the rest of the season. 


Ronnie Karam from Watch What Crappens and Rose Pricks podcast helps Kate review Bachelor Winter Games.
